Ka seener, Buŋ kaawko pey ɗo ɗubil ka Buŋdi rakki aman: " Kiŋke ko Roŋdu, min ƴiriyta-aŋ, nun ko Takko. " Ho ŋa kaaw pey aman: " Nun naa gine Takko ho ŋaar sa yaa gine Roŋdu. "
Wiktin taat Buŋ imiliig roŋji ka awalle ɗo duniiner, ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " *Ɗubal ku Buŋdi okin̰co yaa abdiyin̰ji. "
Ɗo bi ka ɗubal ku Buŋdi-ak, Buŋ kaawiy ɗo bi ka awalle aman: " Ŋa gina ɗubilji ar us kaak abiraw ho ŋa giniy gay riyoy ar ako. "
Kar Buŋ gay kaawiy ɗo bi ka nun Roŋji aman: " Buŋ, kiŋ goy keɗer doo. Meennuwin̰ yaa goye iŋ botilti ho iŋ botilti, ŋaar sellen̰.
Ki elgig maan kaak samaane ho ki ƴilaag maan kaak samaanno. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ, Buŋjiŋ, doɓin̰ciŋ loco pakgig een̰jiŋ ku pey. Ŋa doɓin̰ciŋ iŋ sewe ka galal, kii gine portiko. "
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak, ŋa ɗiytu pey aman: " Rabbine, kiŋ ko kaak kilgiyit duniine min ɗo teesindi. Ho samaan gay, ŋaar riy taat pisin̰ji di.
Ŋuur okin̰co-ak yaa sawle, kar kiŋ gay goy anne. Okin̰co, ŋuu zooɗe ar kesuun taat zooɗe.
Ŋuun̰in̰co ar zimilla ar zimilla, ŋu isa newse ar kesuun taat cigile. Kar kiŋ gay, kiŋ gay rawtaaɗo ho elgin̰ji sa gaasaaɗo tak-tak. "
Ɗubal ku Buŋdi gay, Buŋ kaawji ɗo waa min awalle aman: " As goy ɗo meedar nam wiktin taat naaco gedire ɗo adinen̰, ŋuu gine wer ka lee asin̰jiŋ. "
Ruwwin kuuk ŋu n̰aamtu-ak, okin̰co ŋuur aariɗna kuuk gina riy ɗo geemir, ŋu n̰aamtu a ŋuu gine riy ɗo gee kuuk asa gase jile.
Di ŋaar-ak, illa gii karmiyin̰ samaane taat gi dortu-ata, yampa gii rawte min ɗo botilti.
Kaaw taat *ɗubil ka Buŋdi kaawiite, ya kaaw-at ka seener, ho ay gem kaak poociita ho bal karmiyin̰ji gay, Buŋ yaaji taaɓiyin̰ji.
Yampa, ya gi poociit jile ŋaar-aŋka, maman gii gase jile? Ŋaar Rabbin Buŋ ko kaawinti ja, kar gee kuuk dorig ŋaar-ak gaartu waraŋ ɗo bi kan̰ji.
Buŋ sa gaaraako kadar ŋu talig gee-ak iŋ gamin kuuk ajbay dakina, kuuk gaara gudurre ta Buŋdi ho iŋ gamin kuuk gaara gudurre ta Ruwwiney kuuk Buŋ beriico ɗo geemir uudin taat ŋa rakiyo.
Ŋa Buŋ balco bere ɗo *ɗubal ku Buŋdi a ŋuu goye duniin ta asaw, taar ko taat ŋuu jammiye.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gem rakki kaawtu pey ɗo wer ka Buŋdi aman: " Gem di maa gemir kaak ki moyiy kaƴa, ki pakiriy kaaci?
Ki berjiŋ keɗer kapak ar *darjin ta *ɗubal ku Buŋdi. Ki berjiig iŋ darjin iŋ horoomin,
ho ki diyig gamin okin̰co ɗo asin̰ji. " Iŋ taar-at ko, Buŋ diyig gamin okin̰co ɗo kaay. Iŋ taar-at ko, ŋa bal rasin̰ maan kaak ŋa balji diye kaay. Kar diŋ gay, gi talaagɗo gamin okin̰co ɗo kaay.
Kar gay, gi talaag Iisa. Ŋaar kaak ŋu diyig paayig ɗubal ku Buŋdi sooɗ di. Diŋ gay, ŋa gasit ja *darjiney iŋ darjiney asaan ŋa taaɓiye, ŋaa mate. Iŋ barkin ta Buŋdi, ŋaa taaɓiye, ŋaa mate ɗo bi ka gee okin̰co.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ku iban kadar Buŋ, ŋaar kaak kilgiyig gamin okin̰co ɗo saan tan̰ji ho iŋ ŋaar di, Buŋ yaa taaɓiyin̰ gee dakina a ŋuu gase *darjiney. Paa kat, ŋaa kuuniye botol taat ŋuuco jilin̰co tak-tak iŋ taaɓine.
Ŋaar kaak ginaag gee kuuk sellen̰ ho iŋ ŋuur kuuk sellen̰-ak, okin̰co, ŋuur kun̰co rakki di. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Iisa doraagɗo tak-tak a ŋa kolaag siŋtay.
Ŋa kaawiy ɗo Buŋdi aman: " Naa gaarin̰ siŋjiŋ siŋdu iŋ siŋtan̰. Naa ozile lociŋ ɗo uŋco ka gee okin̰co. "
Kar ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " Nun naa diye gelbiner iŋ ŋaara. " Ŋa ɗiytu pey aman: " Taloŋ, aŋ nun ko-aŋka iŋ koogin kuuk Buŋ beriidu. "
Gee kuuk koogin-ak, ŋuur ar gemo iŋ baarco. Ampaa ko, Iisa oki, ŋaar gintu zi ka gemor. Ŋa gintu pa-ak a ŋaa deen̰ *Seetanne, ŋaar kaak gin gudurre ta muuti. Paa kat, iŋ taaɓiner-ak ko, ŋaa deen̰ Seetanne, ŋaar kaak gin gudurre ka muuti.
ho ŋaa jilin̰ gee kuuk goy ɓerrina ɗo muutco asaan ŋu gina kolaw paa di.
Ka seener gay, ŋa bal paaye *ɗubal ku Buŋdi, ŋa paayig ja. Ŋaar kaak min tamba ta Ibraayim kat paayga.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, illa ŋa ginaaji gine ar siŋtay ɗo ay maanna. Paa kat, ŋaa gine mee satkiner ka tatko kaak sellen̰ ho kaak sellen̰ ɗo riy ta Buŋdi. Ŋaa gine *satkin taat ŋaa gine saamiye ɗo bi ka zunuubinna ku geemir.
Ya ŋaar meen̰ji kat taaɓiy iŋ meen̰ji, Buŋ taaɓiyga ho diŋ ŋa gedarro gaaye ŋuur kuuk Buŋ gecaag gecin̰co.
Gem kol siŋtay, kuŋ kuuk Buŋ doɓtu ho Buŋ koliŋko oki, diyoŋ ɗo gelbinko Iisa Masi. Ŋaar ko *paliine ho ŋaar kaak tatkaw ka gay satkiner ka tatko kaak ni kaawiy biy ɗo geemir.
Ŋa goy sellen̰ ɗo Buŋ kaak doɓga, ar Muusa oki, ŋa goy sellen̰ ɗo geriy okin̰ji ka Buŋdi.
Min pa-ak, Iisa, Buŋ talaag a ŋaar pakgig gem kaak pina ger tatik pakgig Muusa, ar gem kaak pinig ger-ak, ŋaar pakgig ger ka gerdi.
Ka seener gay, ay ger, gem kat pinig gem-aka, kar gay, ŋa Buŋ kat pinig gamin okin̰co.
Muusa gay, ŋaar sellen̰ ɗo riy ta Buŋdi okin̰ji ar gay riyor. Ŋa kaawgiy ɗo geemir a Buŋ yaa kaawe ɗo bi ka gamin kuuk Buŋ yaa kaawe.
Kar gay, Masi gay, ŋaar sellen̰ ar roŋji, ŋa ɗeetaw ɗo adiy ka ger ka Buŋdi. Nin gay, ni geen̰ji di ger ka Buŋdi, ya gi ɗuunit kaaw taat ni diytu kaay ho ni diytu gelbinte iŋ ŋaara.
Ansii ko, taat Ruwwin ta Buŋdi kaawiico aman: " Ƴiriyta-aŋ ya ku cokiyiit gaaƴar,
Dakoŋ tirƴenno kaƴko ar kaak ŋu gintu ƴiriy rakki ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, wiktin taat Buŋ astu gecin̰co ɗo goosiner,
Ɗo wer ŋaar-ak ko, aginiyko gecintu *gaanuun, ŋu gecintu botol taat ŋu gecintu. Ɗo wer-ak ko, ŋu taltu maan kaak nu gintu nam elgin orok pooɗ ŋu taltu.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, nu dapin̰tu ɗo gee ku diŋka ho nu ɗiytu aman: ‟ Ŋu gee ŋuur-aŋ rawte doo iŋ botilco. Ŋu bal ibinin botilnar. "
Ansii ko, nu togiltu iŋ dapin̰du aman: ‟ Ŋu un̰jaaɗo tak-tak ɗo wer kaak nu ɓaayiy goye. " "
Goyoŋ goɗom, gem kol siŋtay, ya minninko rakki ginno gelbin rakki kaak gin zunuubinna, ŋa poocgigɗo imaanko ho ŋa rasiig min ɗo Buŋ kaak goy mento.
Diŋ gay, ɗo wiktin taat Kitamne kaawtu aman: " ‟ Ƴiriyta " di, diŋ gay, iskaakoŋ ziŋkiko doo, paa kat, minninko rakki yaa ɗibire iŋ raadin ta zunuubinnar.
Nin gay, gi goy sawa iŋ Iisa Masi ya ni obit imaanni taat taɓ min ɗo teesindi nam ɗo muutuy.
Ɗo saan taar-at ko, Buŋ ɗiytu pey aman: " Ƴiriyta-aŋ ya ku cokiyiit gaaƴay, dakoŋ tirƴenno kaƴko ar ŋuur kuuk newsiig Buŋ. "
Gee kuuk cokiyit kaawco-at ho ŋu newsiji kaawco ɗo Buŋdi-ak gay waa? Gee-ak, ŋuur okin̰coɗo kuuk Muusa imiliig min Meser di?
Buŋ dapin̰tu iŋ waa nam elgin orok pooɗ ŋa dapin̰tu iŋ ŋuura? Ha'a, illa ŋuur kuuk gin zunuubinna ho muutco mattu ɗo goosiner-aku!
Kar Buŋ togiltu iŋ waa a ŋu un̰jaaɗo ɗo wer kaak ŋa goyiy iŋ ŋaara? Illa ŋa ɗiyco ɗo gee kuuk bal aamine.
Hiyya, ni tala kadar ŋu bal gedire un̰je ɗo wer-aka asaan imaanco sooɗ di.
Gem kaak Buŋ kaawtu a ŋa ɓaa un̰je ɗo wer kaak ŋa beriico goye ɗo ƴiriy rakki, ŋaar-ak goy di misa. Yaman, ya minninko rakki sa bal gase, ŋaa rawte.
Ni iban kadar ŋuur oki gaarinti Kabarre ta Gala ar taat ŋu dortu. Kar gay, kaaw taat ŋu dortu-at balco gaaye maanna, asaan gee kuuk cokiyit kaaw-at, ŋu bal iyin̰ iŋ imaanco.
Nin-aŋ gay, kuŋ kuuk aamine, gi un̰ja ɗo wer kaak ŋa un̰jitu ɗo ƴiriy ta sabitdi-ata. Ar taat Buŋ kaawtu awalle aman: " Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, nu togiltu iŋ dapin̰du aman: ‟ Ŋu un̰jaaɗo tak-tak ɗo wer kaak nu goyiy eɗe. " Ŋaar gay, ka seener, ŋa gaasit ko riy okintiti min kilgiye ka duniiner, ŋa ginit ko riy okintiti.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ kaawtu maanna ɗo wer rakki ɗo bi ka ƴiriy ta peesira ho ŋa kaawtu ampa-ak aman: " Kar ƴiriy ta peesir-at gay, Buŋ jammiytu min ɗo riy okintit taat ŋa gintu. "
Ansii ko, ŋu siirtu pey ɗo Kitamner aman: " Ŋu un̰jaaɗo tak-tak ɗo wer kaak nu goyiy eɗe. "
Ansii ko, pey botol taat Buŋ yaa un̰jin̰ gee ku pey ɗo imaanco. Kar ŋuur kuuk awalle gasit Kabarre ta Gala gay, ŋu bal gedire un̰je asaan ŋu bal ooyin̰ji.
Buŋ kat diytu pey ƴiriy rakki taat ŋaa n̰aame. Ƴiriy taar-at ko, Buŋ kaawtu min ɗo Dawuud min daayum a ŋaa gine. Ŋa kaawtu awalle aman: " Ƴiriy taar-an, ya ku cokiy gaaƴar, dakoŋ tirƴenno kaƴko. "
Zer, ya Zoozuwe kat un̰jitu ɗo gee kuuk goy ɗo ger ka Buŋdi-ak, Buŋ bal kaawe pey ƴiriy rakki ta pey.
Min ŋaar-ak, Buŋ goy misa eɗe ɗo gee kuuk goy ɗo riyoy ta sabitdi. Ŋaar gay goy pey ƴiriy rakki ta sabitdi taat ŋa ɗeettu ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Asaan gem kaak un̰jitu ɗo eɗe ka Buŋdi gay, ŋaar oki jammiytu min ɗo riy taat ŋa gintu, ar Buŋ oki jammiytu min ɗo riy ta meen̰ji.
Gem kol siŋtay, gi ɓaa un̰je ɗo wer kaak ŋa ɗeettu okiɗ-aka. Yampa, waan yaa gase baati ar ŋuur kuuk pooc karmiyiigu.
Kaaw ta Buŋdi, taar goy mento ho ta gin gudurre. Taar pakgig seepinpan okin̰ji kuuk cewey seerco. Ta un̰ja ɗo adiy ka gemor nam ta eergig goyin̰ji, eɗe iŋ ruwwine, ɗo amiydi ho ɗo morginay. Ta n̰aamaaniite ginte sellen̰ nam gii ibinin̰ ziŋkini.
Gamin okin̰co kuuk Buŋ kilgiyig cigile, ŋa ibanno. Gamin okin̰co goy cigile, ŋu tallo tak-tak ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, ŋaar kaak gii ose biŋkico.
Min ŋaar-ak, ni gin mee satkiner ka tatko kaak tatiko, ŋaar Iisa, Roŋ ka Buŋdi, ŋaar un̰jitu kuwa ka samaaner. Diŋ gay, obig samaane ɗo kaaw taat ni ooyiita.
Ka seener, mee satkiner ka tatko kaak ni ginno, ŋaar kaak ibanno nigin̰ji. Ŋaar gay, Buŋ gecaag ɗo ay maanna ar ginte kuuk ŋu gecaag ginte. Kar gay, ŋaar ginno zunuubinna.
Diŋ gay, sin̰jinte iŋ gelbin rakki ɗo sees ka Buŋdi kaak ŋa obit barkin min ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Gi ɓaawe iŋ gelbin rakki a ŋaa gase aminduwni ho gii gase barkin taat yaa gaaye ɗo wiktin taat yaa nece.
Ay mee satkiner ka tatko, ŋu doɓta min ɗo ɗatik ta geemir ho ŋa diyiig ɗo bi ka gee ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi a ŋaa gine *satkin iŋ gamin, ŋaa gine *satkin ɗo Buŋdi ho ŋaa gine *satkin ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar.
Kar mee satkiner ka tatko-ak gay, ŋaar raɗa a ŋaa aaɗe iŋ gelbin rakki iŋ gee kuuk ibanno maanna ho kuuk rawte.
Ɗo saan taar-at ko, ŋaa gine *satkine ɗo bi ka meen̰ji di ho ɗo bi ka zunuubinna ku geemir oki.
Ginno gem kaak nec icin̰ ziŋkico a ŋaa goye tatkaw-aka, illa Buŋ kat koliig ŋaar di ar kaak Buŋ koliig *Haruun.
Ansii ko, Masi oki, ŋaar bal bariye kaay tak-tak darjin ta meen̰ji a ŋaa gine mee satkiner ka tatko. Ŋaar gay, ŋa Buŋ kat kaawji aman: " Kiŋke-aŋ ko Roŋdu, min ƴiriyta-aŋ, nun ko Takko. "
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ kaawtu pey ɗo wer ka pey aman: " Kiŋ mee satkiner kaak yaa goye doo ar Melsi-Seetanne. "
Ɗo wiktin taat Iisa goyiy misa ɗo duniiner, ŋa teestu inde Buŋ iŋ zulin̰ji ho ŋa teestu inde buŋ iŋ zulin̰ji. Ŋa indiiji Buŋ iŋ marmile ho ŋa altu inde tak-tak. Kar Buŋ sa cokiyiiga asaan ŋa zeeɗiy sooɗa.
Sando, ŋaar gay roŋ ka Buŋdi, kar ŋa karmiyiit kaaw ta taaɓiner ho ŋa karmiyiy maan kaak ŋa taaɓiytu.
Min ŋa gintu *cawar, ŋa gintu botol taat ŋaa gase jile ka gaasɗo ɗo gee okin̰co kuuk karmiyaaga.
Buŋ kat doɓga a ŋa gine *mee satkiner ka tatko ar kaak ŋu koliy Melsi-Seedek.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak, ni gin kaawin dakina kuuk nii kaawin dakina, kar kaawin ŋuur-ak gay raɗa a ŋuu gaarin̰co, asaan kuŋ gee kuuk ɗeŋginko bombo.
Ya kuŋ kat raka gine tatkuwko, illa ku raka gem yaako ɓildiŋko pey min ɗo kaaw ta Buŋdi. Ku raka pey gem kaak yaako ɓildiŋko min kuwa. Illa ku raka tee kaak taɓ, ku raka tee kaak taɓ.
Ya gem kaak tiya tiya saa, ŋaar ar mico di. Ŋaar ibanno maan kaak sellen̰, ŋaar ar koogin kuuk misa.
Kar tee kaak ɗak-ak gay, ŋaar ɗo gee kuuk aginiyji, ŋuur kuuk gin gudurre taat ŋuu ibinin imaanco, ŋuu ibinin̰ maan kaak samaane iŋ kaak samaane.
Di ŋaar-ak, gi ɓaa gine gee kuuk neenduway. Gii ice pey kaawin kuuk samaane kuuk kaawa ɗo bi ka Masi. Gii ice pey kaawin kuuk gaara muutur kuuk gaara muutuy di ho gii diye imaanco ɗo Buŋdi.
Kar *gaanuun ka aginiyte sa, ni ɓildaagɗo pey gee ɗo bi ka *batiziyennar, ɗo bi ka lee pise ka geemir, ɗo bi ka nooyindi ho ɗo bi ka gee kuuk mate, ho ɗo bi ka seriin ta Buŋdi oki.
Kar gay, ya Buŋ kat raka, gii ibinin̰ pey tak-tak.
Ŋuur-ak gay, ŋu gas portikaw ta Buŋdi, ŋu cale maan kaak Buŋ beriico, ŋu gas Ruwwin ta Buŋdi oki.
Ŋuur kuuk rasit kaaw ta Buŋdi ho gasit gudurre ta gamin kuuk yaa ase.
Ka seener gay, ya ŋu pooc ɗeete, ŋu gediraaɗo pey ŋuu ibinin̰ nigin̰co pey ɗo imaanco, asaan ŋu raka ɗooɗin̰ nun Roŋ ka Buŋdi ka etor pey ho ŋu gaara kadar nu Roŋ ka Buŋdi ka etor iŋ uŋco ka geemir.
Ya kiɗ kaak cokaw amay kuuk n̰okaag kun kawta ho ŋa imilgiy roŋ kuuk samaane ɗo gee kuuk ŋu luwiy-ak, Buŋ barkiyiig kiɗ-aka.
Kar kiɗ kaak wiyaw busam kuuk gin jamay iŋ pompal kuuk gin jamay gay, ŋaar n̰aamgigɗo. Ŋaar-ak, Buŋ yaako surpiyin̰ji. Ba aaro, ŋuu orin̰ ɗo aki.
Gem kol siŋtay, ya ni kaawa ampa-ak sa, ni iban kadar ku gina gamin kuuk samaane ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ho kuŋ gee kuuk asa gase jile.
Buŋ, ŋaar sellen̰ ɗo maan kaak ŋa rawtiɗo. Ŋa rawtiitɗo riy taat ku gintu ho elin̰ taat ku gaartu ɗo uŋji, asaan ku ginit riyoy ɗo geen̰ji ho diŋ sa ku gaayɗo pey.
Kar nin raka a ay gem di yaa gaare gelbin rakki paa nam ɗo muutuy, ansii kat, kuu ibine kadar imaan taat ku gintu-an ka seener.
Nu rakaaɗo kuu goye mogina, kar gay, ni rakaaɗo kuu gine gee kuuk asaan ŋu obit kaaw taat Buŋ kaawtu a ŋuu gase. Ŋuur gay, iŋ imaanco ho iŋ imaanco taat ŋu gintu subba di, ŋuu gase gamin kuuk Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaco bere.
Wiktin taat Buŋ togiltu iŋ Ibraayim, ŋa togiltu iŋ ŋaara asaan ginno waan kaak pakgigɗo.
Ŋa kaawtu aman: " Ka seener, naan̰ barkiyin̰ciŋ ho naan̰ miinin̰ dakina. "
Ampaa ko, Ibraayim ictu riyoy iŋ imaan ta Buŋdi. Hiyya, ŋa gastu maan kaak Buŋ kaawiiji a ŋaaji bere.
Ya gee togila, ŋu togila iŋ gem kaak tatik pakgig ŋuura. Ya ŋu togila, kaawoy yaa gaare kadar kaaw okintit kaawco goy iŋ Buŋ, ho kaaw-at yaa gaase baati.
Buŋ raka gaare waraŋ ɗo gee kuuk yaa gase kaaw taat ŋa kaawiico. Ŋa raka gaare kadar kaaw-at tallo tak-tak. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ togiltu pey a kaaw-at yaa goye paa di.
Buŋ, ŋaar kaawa seene. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, kaaw seer goy doo. Nin-aŋ barayɗo maan kaak Buŋ kaawtu. Paa kat, gi ɓaa icit kaaw taat ŋa kaawinti a ŋuu goye bombo iŋ gelbin rakki.
Kar gay, ni gin imaan taat bera goye ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ar zimilla kuuk bera goye ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Zimilla-ak, ŋu un̰jaaɗo atta ɗo wer kaak *cawar aale.
Ɗo wer ŋaar-ak, Iisa ogirinti ko ɗo saan tan̰ji. Ŋa ginig *mee satkiner ka tatko kaak tatko ar Melsizeedek nam taa goye doo.
Gem-ak, siŋji Melsi-Sadek, ŋaar ko sultan ka Salaam ho ŋa gay satkiner ka Buŋ ka kuwa. Ŋaar ko kaak ɓaa ŋaamin̰ Ibraayim ɗo wiktin taat ŋa yeeptu min riyco ka sultinniidi ho ŋa barkiyiiga.
Ibraayim gay berji zakaane min ɗo gamnay okin̰co kuuk ŋa gidiyiiga. (Siŋ kuuk ŋu kolaag Melsi-Seedek-ak ɗiya a " sultan ka goye ka seener. " Kar Seleem gay, siŋ ku Seleem-ak ɗiya a " aapiye." Ŋaar oki ɗiya a " sultan ka aapiyer."
Ŋa ginno tak-tak, wala iŋ aginiyji, wala ŋa ginno koogin ku aginiydi, wala ŋa ween̰ji, wala ŋa gaasɗo. Ŋaar ar Roŋ ka Buŋdi ho ŋa goy gay satkiner tak-tak.
Taloŋ ja, tatkaw kaak ŋu kolaag Melsizeek-aŋ tatik aale! Ibraayim oki berji zakaane min gamin kuuk ŋa gaamtu min ɗo gamin okin̰co kuuk ŋa gaamtu min ɗo jineendi.
*Gaanuun kaawco ɗo gee kuuk gina satkiner min tamba ta Lebi a ŋuu icin̰ zakaane min ɗo geemir, ŋuur min ɗo siŋco ku maaniico, yoo siŋco kuuk min tamba ta Ibraayim di.
