Gamin ŋaar-ak ko, ŋaar di mee satkiner ka tatko kaak gi raka: ŋaar *cawar, ŋa bal nige *cawar, ŋa bal nige gallo ar ginte kuuk gin zunuubinna. Ho ŋaar gay, kaay pakgig gamin kuuk goy kuwa ka samaaner.
