Ŋu gina riy taat ŋu giniy riy ɗo *ger ka Buŋdi. Wer-ak gay, ŋaar n̰aamgig di maan kaak ar maan kaak kuwa ka samaaner. Ɗo saan taar-at ko, Buŋ miniig Muusa wiktin taat ŋa gaay pine gerdi a ŋaa pinin̰ji. Ŋa kaawiiji ɗo Buŋdi aman: " Pakiroŋ samaane, kii gine gamin okin̰co ar kaak nu gaariijiŋ ka damba-aŋka. "
